values:
&nbsp;So i worked tonight, not a big deal, not at all. The same thing night after night i go in.Oh well, i guess i should be thankful for some kind oconstant in my life right?&nbsp;

Besides that boringness, my love life is slowly getting more and more confusing. I feel so many different ways about different people. And then its like the one of two that i really wanna be with i can't , they either have someone, or its just too late. I feel like my love life is spiraling into hell. I hate it, i hate it soooo much, i wish i just had....her, i wish so much. I feel so helpless. Should i even feel this way, houldn't i just suck it up., move on and up to something better, or not? I can't answer that question, should i be able to? Ugh.....I need her, but she has someone, i want to be her friend, i wanna just be here for her, but then again, i wanna tell her that am totally falling in love with her, that i want to be with her more than anything right now. The worst thing is , that i have no idea what she thinks of me, is that terrible, i mean i can tell myself at she likes me, but i am so unsure that its killing me. Ugh....women......me......not a good mix apparently. Help.....


So i am almost finished x-mas shopping, so thats a good thing, i still have my dad, sister, and a few others to go. SO that is a good thing. I notice that i have a few random good things, which is better than none, Oh and i am finished with my first semester of COLLEGE !!!! yay me!!! , hey , i am excited...!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!1


OK, well, if i don't hear from any of you guys over break, i hope you all have a wonderful break, and christmas.&nbsp;

love and peace,
T

So&nbsp;two. well,&nbsp;three now, days have&nbsp;ge by since my last post. Things are not any better. Work, School, Finals.Yum.

That is all, nothing has changed.


T&nbsp;

&nbsp;The best part of grauating high school is that you get to be you. I mean you get to be your own person for once, especially if you go from your parents house our own apartment.It is so nice to get off a hard nights work and just come HOME, you know, your home. I like the responsibility, weird huh?&nbsp;

Anways, as you can tell i finally got my interent set up at home, so thats good. I missed the net at home. So work is going good, i just got paid, so i am joyous. School, is well, school, you know homework and stuff, same ole same ole.&nbsp;

Onto the good stuff. I love you i really do, i always will.I swear to the God i don't even believe in. I will love you always and forever, no matter how our lives end up, you could be a thousand miles aways, and forget my name, but yours will always have a special place in my heart, and that mark on me will never leave. Whether i get to be a part of your life or not, i am always here, unti the day i die.&nbsp;

I know , i know, hopeless romantic, blah blah blah......thats me so, if you don't like it.....well.........bluntly......fuck off....the end.


xoxoxo

So i just finished getting my apartment together, now all i need is a desk. I think i am getting a new pet soon, but its hard to decide what to get. I really would like a little ferret, but i am not&nbsp;sure yet. Any suggestions?&nbsp;

Anways, Halloween was, just another day for me, and now that i think about it, i didn't have a single piece of candy on Halloween, how bad is that? I have&nbsp;work the rest of the week, which i guess is good, i will stay busy at least. My job is going ok i guess, i am told that i am doing a good job, so&nbsp;thats good. I am finallly getting my own internet too, which is wonderful. I feel like all big things in my life are coming together, like my apartment, and school. I do feel a little distraught emotionally though, and i can't figure it out.Maybe i am just going crazy or something????Who knows.........Besides all these things, i am making a few more friends, so&nbsp;that is always good.&nbsp;Gotta run,&nbsp;talk to you guys later.

-travis&nbsp;

